### Create SPU with SKUs (Clothing - Color + Size variations)
POST {{url_dev}}/v1/product/spu/new
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{api_key}}
authorization: {{access_token}}
x-client-id: {{client_id}}

{
  "product_name": "Classic Cotton T-Shirt",
  "product_thumb": "https://example.com/images/tshirt.jpg",
  "product_description": "Premium cotton t-shirt available in multiple colors and sizes",
  "product_price": 29.99,
  "product_quantity": 300,
  "product_category": ["fashion", "clothing"],
  "product_attributes": {
    "brand": "Nike",
    "material": "100% Cotton",
    "care": "Machine washable"
  },
  "product_variations": [
    {
      "name": "color",
      "images": ["https://example.com/images/red.jpg", "https://example.com/images/blue.jpg"],
      "options": ["red", "blue"]
    },
    {
      "name": "size",
      "images": [],
      "options": ["S", "M", "L"]
    }
  ],
  "sku_list": [
    {
      "sku_tier_idx": [0, 0],
      "sku_default": true,
      "sku_price": 29.99,
      "sku_stock": 50
    },
    {
      "sku_tier_idx": [0, 1],
      "sku_default": false,
      "sku_price": 29.99,
      "sku_stock": 50
    },
    {
      "sku_tier_idx": [0, 2],
      "sku_default": false,
      "sku_price": 29.99,
      "sku_stock": 50
    },
    {
      "sku_tier_idx": [1, 0],
      "sku_default": false,
      "sku_price": 29.99,
      "sku_stock": 50
    },
    {
      "sku_tier_idx": [1, 1],
      "sku_default": false,
      "sku_price": 29.99,
      "sku_stock": 50
    },
    {
      "sku_tier_idx": [1, 2],
      "sku_default": false,
      "sku_price": 29.99,
      "sku_stock": 50
    }
  ]
}

###

### Create SPU without SKUs (no variations)
POST {{url_dev}}/v1/product/spu/new
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{api_key}}
authorization: {{access_token}}
x-client-id: {{client_id}}

{
  "product_name": "Wireless Bluetooth Headphones",
  "product_thumb": "https://example.com/images/headphones.jpg",
  "product_description": "Over-ear noise cancelling headphones with 30h battery life",
  "product_price": 149.99,
  "product_quantity": 80,
  "product_category": ["electronics", "audio"],
  "product_attributes": {
    "brand": "Sony",
    "model": "WH-1000XM5",
    "connectivity": "Bluetooth 5.2",
    "battery": "30 hours"
  },
  "product_variations": [],
  "sku_list": []
}

###

### Get SPU with its SKUs
# Replace {spu_id} with the product_id returned from the create call above
GET {{url_dev}}/v1/product/spu/{spu_id}
x-api-key: {{api_key}}
authorization: {{access_token}}
x-client-id: {{client_id}}

###

### Get SPU again - should be served from Redis cache (check response for fromCache: true)
GET {{url_dev}}/v1/product/spu/{spu_id}
x-api-key: {{api_key}}
authorization: {{access_token}}
x-client-id: {{client_id}}

###

### Get all SKUs by SPU id
GET {{url_dev}}/v1/product/sku/{spu_id}/all
x-api-key: {{api_key}}
authorization: {{access_token}}
x-client-id: {{client_id}}

###

### Get a single SKU by product_id and sku_id (first request - DB hit, populates cache)
# Replace {spu_id} with product_id and {sku_id} with a sku_id from the create response
GET {{url_dev}}/v1/product/sku/{spu_id}/{sku_id}
x-api-key: {{api_key}}
authorization: {{access_token}}
x-client-id: {{client_id}}

###

### Get same SKU again - should be served from Redis cache (fromCache: true)
GET {{url_dev}}/v1/product/sku/{spu_id}/{sku_id}
x-api-key: {{api_key}}
authorization: {{access_token}}
x-client-id: {{client_id}}
